      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition. The exterior shows some noticeable scratches and a small dent on the rear bumper. The interior has visible wear on the seats and carpet, though it remains intact. The engine and transmission are operational, but the vehicle will likely require routine maintenance soon.",
